title: Lunchbox Reveals He Missed Something About His Rocks + Elder Vs. Millennial Returns! + Eddie Was Wildly Famous for A Day…How Were You Famous For A Day?
itunes:title: Lunchbox Reveals He Missed Something About His Rocks + Elder Vs. Millennial Returns! + Eddie Was Wildly Famous for A Day…How Were You Famous For A Day?
description:
Lunchbox shares that he missed something from the rocks he brought home from his Diamond mining trip. He thinks a couple of them are worth big money! We bring back Elder vs. Millennial with Eddie going up against Morgan2 in a battle of generational trivia. Eddie reveals that he made the news back in the day and was famous for a day! We take calls from other people who were famous for a day and they get pretty interesting.
